  <brief_title>The Effects of Lactobacillus Plantarum on Cortisol, IgA and Alpha-amylase Levels in Human Saliva During Stress</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Lactobacillus Plantarum on Cortisol, IgA and Alpha-amylase Levels in Human Saliva During Stress</official_title>
